---
/* Astro Component Script */
---
<section class="process bg-white text-black py-16 px-6">
    <!-- Trusted Brands Section -->
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase">Brands We Trust for Remodeling in Maryland</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-13">
            <img src="public/company1.png" alt="Moen" class="h-10" />
            <img src="public/company2.png" alt="American Standard" class="h-10" />
            <img src="public/company3.png" alt="Delta" class="h-10" />
            <img src="public/company4.png" alt="Sherwin-Williams" class="h-10" />
            <img src="public/company5.png" alt="Kohler" class="h-10" />
            <img src="public/company7.png" alt="KraftMaid" class="h-10" />
        </div>
    </div>



    <!-- Remodeling Process Section -->
    <section class="bg-gray-100 py-16">
        <div class="max-w-[75%] mx-auto">
            <!-- Title and Description -->
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-start lg:items-center justify-between mb-12">
                <!-- Title -->
                <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 lg:mb-0 lg:mr-8 text-left">
                    Our Remodeling <br /> Process
                </h2>
                <!-- Subtitle -->
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-justify lg:max-w-[40%]">
                    We follow a clear, client-focused process to ensure every remodeling project is completed
                    on time, on budget, and with high-quality results.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Process Steps -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 relative">
                <!-- Step 1 -->
                <div class="text-center relative">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <img src="public/process1.png" alt="Project Consultation & Planning" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full" />
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Project Consultation & Planning</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-justify">
                        We start by listening to your goals, needs, and vision. Whether you're remodeling your kitchen, bathroom, or entire home, we define the scope, timeline, and budget.
                    </p>
                    <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-px bg-gray-300 hidden lg:block"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 2 -->
                <div class="text-center relative">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <img src="public/process2.png" alt="Design & Material Selection" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full" />
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Design & Material Selection</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-justify">
                        Once we understand your goals, we move into the design phase. We'll help you choose layouts, finishes, colors, fixtures, tiles, flooring, and cabinetry that match your style and budget.
                    </p>
                    <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-px bg-gray-300 hidden lg:block"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 3 -->
                <div class="text-center relative">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <img src="public/process3.png" alt="Construction & Installation" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full" />
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Construction & Installation</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-justify">
                        Now it’s time to bring the plan to life. Our team begins the construction process — from demolition to framing, plumbing, electrical, drywall, and installation.
                    </p>
                    <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-px bg-gray-300 hidden lg:block"></div>
                </div>
                <!-- Step 4 -->
                <div class="text-center relative">
                    <div class="mb-4">
                        <img src="public/process4.png" alt="Final Walkthrough & Quality Check" class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-full" />
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Final Walkthrough & Quality Check</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-justify">
                        Once construction is complete, we do a full walkthrough together to make sure every detail meets your expectations.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <a href="#start-remodel" class="inline-block bg-black text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm hover:bg-gray-800">
                Let’s Start Your Remodel →
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>